      <akn:section eId="sec_5_1501_11">
        <akn:num>5-1501.11</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Science Advisory Board.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_5-1501_11_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>There is established a Science Advisory Board, which shall consist of 9 voting members to be appointed pursuant to ยง 1-523.01(f), as follows:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_5-1501_11_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The Director and Deputy Director shall be ex officio, non-voting members of the Board.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_5-1501_11_c">
      <akn:num>(c)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p></akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_5-1501_11_d">
      <akn:num>(d)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The Board shall elect a chairperson from among its voting members.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_5-1501_11_e">
      <akn:num>(e)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The presence of a majority of the voting members holding office shall constitute a quorum.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_5-1501_11_f">
      <akn:num>(f)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The Board shall hold no fewer than 4 regular meetings per year. The chairperson of the Board shall fix the time and place of each meeting. Additional meetings may be called either by the chairperson or upon the written request of the Director or of any 3 members of the Board.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_5-1501_11_g">
      <akn:num>(g)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Minutes shall be prepared for each meeting. A transcript or detailed summary shall meet this requirement.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
